(857, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/pNHv41t8Im8wlwgdzMK9I8WpuBZ.jpg', '18,36,10752', 'en', 'As U.S. troops storm the beaches of Normandy, three brothers lie dead on the battlefield, with a fourth trapped behind enemy lines. Ranger captain John Miller and seven men are tasked with penetrating German-held territory and bringing the boy home.', '60.971', '/1wY4psJ5NVEhCuOYROwLH2XExM2.jpg', '1998-07-24', 'Saving Private Ryan', 'false', '8.2', 13647),
(862, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/3Rfvhy1Nl6sSGJwyjb0QiZzZYlB.jpg', '16,12,10751,35', 'en', 'Led by Woody, Andy\'s toys live happily in his room until Andy\'s birthday brings Buzz Lightyear onto the scene. Afraid of losing his place in Andy\'s heart, Woody plots against Buzz. But when circumstances separate Buzz and Woody from their owner, the duo eventually learns to put aside their differences.', '135.779', '/uXDfjJbdP4ijW5hWSBrPrlKpxab.jpg', '1995-10-30', 'Toy Story', 'false', '8.0', 16049),
(872, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/g7KmJaGFvST5cyvA71V6epKAqIC.jpg', '35,10402,10749,18', 'en', 'In 1927 Hollywood, a silent film production company and cast make a difficult transition to sound.', '23.392', '/671EPwBsHGHBk0cdOeZqmOK0XB3.jpg', '1952-04-09', 'Singin\' in the Rain', 'false', '8.2', 2574),
(895, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/fKa8Jy2ge1O0IU6zZXnJ2sxUzdU.jpg', '18,36', 'ru', 'An expansive Russian drama, this film focuses on the life of revered religious icon painter Andrei Rublev. Drifting from place to place in a tumultuous era, the peace-seeking monk eventually gains a reputation for his art. But after Rublev witnesses a brutal battle and unintentionally becomes involved, he takes a vow of silence and spends time away from his work. As he begins to ease his troubled soul, he takes steps towards becoming a painter once again.', '17.858', '/910xRIUmNJrWH2hkQifBJtoPp5R.jpg', '1966-12-16', 'Andrei Rublev', 'false', '8.1', 616),
(901, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/n0Cju2Eu3VyrUFl32thblHFWznA.jpg', '35,18,10749', 'en', 'In this sound-era silent film, a tramp falls in love with a beautiful blind flower seller.', '18.747', '/bXNvzjULc9jrOVhGfjcc64uKZmZ.jpg', '1931-02-01', 'City Lights', 'false', '8.3', 1744),
(914, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/8AMKZODrCvWe2sCy9Ts7VsLcKd6.jpg', '35,10752', 'en', 'Dictator Adenoid Hynkel tries to expand his empire while a poor Jewish barber tries to avoid persecution from Hynkel\'s regime.', '24.121', '/1QpO9wo7JWecZ4NiBuu625FiY1j.jpg', '1940-10-15', 'The Great Dictator', 'false', '8.4', 2756),
(935, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/sTp8K0SfcC2RQef1Tu160z3niHO.jpg', '18,35,10752', 'en', 'After the insane General Jack D. Ripper initiates a nuclear strike on the Soviet Union, a war room full of politicians, generals and a Russian diplomat all frantically try to stop the nuclear strike.', '21.990', '/7SixLzxcqezkZEYU8pcHZgbkmjp.jpg', '1964-01-29', 'Dr. Strangelove or: How I Learned to Stop Worrying and Love the Bomb', 'false', '8.1', 4717),
(938, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/f61COvOzOOIwx7whPl5Yj78s9gY.jpg', '37', 'it', 'Two bounty hunters are in pursuit of \"El Indio,\" one of the most wanted fugitives in the western territories, and his gang.', '25.134', '/ooqASvA7qxlTVKL3KwOzBwy57Dh.jpg', '1965-12-18', 'For a Few Dollars More', 'false', '8.0', 3270),
(947, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/mx2jS5Kaa5rmaldEFzKeKpDN9Q2.jpg', '12,18,36,10752', 'en', 'The story of British officer T.E. Lawrence\'s mission to aid the Arab tribes in their revolt against the Ottoman Empire during the First World War. Lawrence becomes a flamboyant, messianic figure in the cause of Arab unity but his psychological instability threatens to undermine his achievements.', '26.518', '/AiAm0EtDvyGqNpVoieRw4u65vD1.jpg', '1962-12-11', 'Lawrence of Arabia', 'false', '8.0', 2433),
(961, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/h68ilwiTesb5wmDgy2mHYkVuOBP.jpg', '28,12,35,18,10752', 'en', 'During America’s Civil War, Union spies steal engineer Johnnie Gray\'s beloved locomotive, \'The General\'—with Johnnie\'s lady love aboard an attached boxcar—and he single-handedly must do all in his power to both get The General back and to rescue Annabelle.', '11.840', '/iaV7LKAEialeaKDtf22SrYMqeFC.jpg', '1926-12-25', 'The General', 'false', '8.0', 951),
(962, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/hZHeDPQGNKN9NN9GuW7qVbM2tDx.jpg', '12,35,18', 'en', 'A lone prospector ventures into Alaska looking for gold. He soon gets mixed up with some burly characters, falls in love with the beautiful Georgia, and tries to win her heart with his singular charm.', '16.280', '/eQRFo1qwRREYwj47Yoe1PisgOle.jpg', '1925-07-12', 'The Gold Rush', 'false', '8.0', 1268),
(975, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/354kfjVb96mtFALMhBE6jzHGiA2.jpg', '18,10752', 'en', 'A commanding officer defends three scapegoats on trial for a failed offensive that occurred within the French Army in 1916.', '18.387', '/l2IY0gOHHmCWM90LjteFssxIV1G.jpg', '1957-10-25', 'Paths of Glory', 'false', '8.3', 2325),
(992, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/v2SCnNZDZ7USonAWnsGtL4PUqHt.jpg', '28,35,9648', 'en', 'A film projectionist longs to be a detective, and puts his meagre skills to work when he is framed by a rival for stealing his girlfriend\'s father\'s pocketwatch.', '13.903', '/1G9r3rqtbFAQuyWKOZm4Y5J5s7Q.jpg', '1924-04-17', 'Sherlock Jr.', 'false', '8.1', 730),
(996, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/u546kDNwrZ1ii6q8NqqQgHwRvoW.jpg', '80,18,9648,53', 'en', 'A rich woman and a calculating insurance agent plot to kill her unsuspecting husband after he signs a double indemnity policy. Against a backdrop of distinctly Californian settings, the partners in crime plan the perfect murder to collect the insurance, which pays double if the death is accidental.', '19.139', '/kkfKLeOTo7RjS9TxHKpknlL7huS.jpg', '1944-06-14', 'Double Indemnity', 'false', '8.1', 1445),
(1059, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/aYD6bR1xs9OAK3lA5WHbvIX2gMN.jpg', '12,18,28,35', 'ja', 'Japanese peasants Matashichi and Tahei try and fail to make a profit from a tribal war. They find a man and woman whom they believe are simple tribe members hiding in a fortress. Although the peasants don\'t know that Rokurota is a general and Yuki is a princess, the peasants agree to accompany the pair to safety in return for gold. Along the way, the general must prove his expertise in battle while also hiding his identity.', '15.198', '/ccGA4zIC6EAsFWUlCqaFEcznWA2.jpg', '1958-12-28', 'The Hidden Fortress', 'false', '8.0', 470),
(1091, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/3eb63ISwxqVaJbSbkgUNfrfB2NS.jpg', '27,9648,878', 'en', 'A team of American scientists investigate the empty, destroyed base of their Norwegian counterparts in Antarctica, only to discover a terrifying life force that can take the form of its prey.', '41.780', '/tzGY49kseSE9QAKk47uuDGwnSCu.jpg', '1982-06-25', 'The Thing', 'false', '8.0', 5672),
(1092, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/mYI1VlxvuSnHoK6GYwkFzAgcJXh.jpg', '53,9648', 'en', 'In postwar Vienna, Austria, Holly Martins, a writer of pulp Westerns, arrives penniless as a guest of his childhood chum Harry Lime, only to learn he has died. Martins develops a conspiracy theory after learning of a \"third man\" present at the time of Harry\'s death, running into interference from British officer Major Calloway, and falling head-over-heels for Harry\'s grief-stricken lover, Anna.', '16.624', '/oIF3l7Dxp7Eyye10BNyM611wtKa.jpg', '1949-08-31', 'The Third Man', 'false', '8.0', 1460),
(1124, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/mfJepkInUbiZ0mFXFhDNz8ko6Zr.jpg', '18,9648,878', 'en', 'A mysterious story of two magicians whose intense rivalry leads them on a life-long battle for supremacy -- full of obsession, deceit and jealousy with dangerous and deadly consequences.', '33.564', '/bdN3gXuIZYaJP7ftKK2sU0nPtEA.jpg', '2006-10-19', 'The Prestige', 'false', '8.2', 13628),
(1396, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/5t3ObSn7mRi2QpV9Rs7heb3y9rJ.jpg', '18,36', 'ru', 'A dying man in his forties recalls his childhood, his mother, the war and personal moments that tell of and juxtapose pivotal moments in Soviet history with daily life.', '17.571', '/AttDP5OEsMxtHPPN7Z92p2Ntnmd.jpg', '1975-03-07', 'Mirror', 'false', '8.0', 726),
(1398, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/xhet9FxP6VoRdlBSsfc9FhCsKSW.jpg', '878,18', 'ru', 'Near a gray and unnamed city is the Zone, a place guarded by barbed wire and soldiers, and where the normal laws of physics are victim to frequent anomalies. A stalker guides two men into the Zone, specifically to an area in which deep-seated desires are granted.', '23.477', '/lUE0Bp7wH0EterJ44qMRsqtKFnp.jpg', '1979-05-25', 'Stalker', 'false', '8.2', 1674),
(1422, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/9RuC3UD6mNZ0p1J6RbfJDUkQ03i.jpg', '18,53,80', 'en', 'To take down South Boston\'s Irish Mafia, the police send in one of their own to infiltrate the underworld, not realizing the syndicate has done likewise. While an undercover cop curries favor with the mob kingpin, a career criminal rises through the police ranks. But both sides soon discover there\'s a mole among them.', '36.813', '/kWWAt2FMRbqLFFy8o5R4Zr8cMAb.jpg', '2006-10-04', 'The Departed', 'false', '8.2', 12909),
(1578, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/tvNuhRlpRozDgsX1zR9gQ2aHv1X.jpg', '18,36', 'en', 'The life of boxer Jake LaMotta, whose violence and temper that led him to the top in the ring destroyed his life outside of it.', '20.010', '/rEviyDWNbAFmvvCPlkMRPAGUElG.jpg', '1980-11-14', 'Raging Bull', 'false', '8.0', 3528),
(1580, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/81LX4wktTXWEXjLNlkHTmJm7tRu.jpg', '80,18,53', 'en', 'Two men attempt to prove they committed the perfect crime by hosting a dinner party after strangling their former classmate to death.', '16.767', '/j6jYX3IO49Z1U20sViIEsQfAI10.jpg', '1948-03-11', 'Rope', 'false', '8.0', 2178),
(1585, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/ch3lDc4xQ9MpsNEpnRhvR8PIxxK.jpg', '18,10751,14', 'en', 'A holiday favourite for generations...  George Bailey has spent his entire life giving to the people of Bedford Falls.  All that prevents rich skinflint Mr. Potter from taking over the entire town is George\'s modest building and loan company.  But on Christmas Eve the business\'s $8,000 is lost and George\'s troubles begin.', '40.446', '/bSqt9rhDZx1Q7UZ86dBPKdNomp2.jpg', '1946-12-20', 'It\'s a Wonderful Life', 'false', '8.3', 3495),
(1891, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/dMZxEdrWIzUmUoOz2zvmFuutbj7.jpg', '12,28,878', 'en', 'The epic saga continues as Luke Skywalker, in hopes of defeating the evil Galactic Empire, learns the ways of the Jedi from aging master Yoda. But Darth Vader is more determined than ever to capture Luke. Meanwhile, rebel leader Princess Leia, cocky Han Solo, Chewbacca, and droids C-3PO and R2-D2 are thrown into various stages of capture, betrayal and despair.', '32.982', '/2l05cFWJacyIsTpsqSgH0wQXe4V.jpg', '1980-05-20', 'The Empire Strikes Back', 'false', '8.4', 14777),
(1955, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/8dfDnaDKLKxtpvqTQM3F4hMgvOM.jpg', '18,36', 'en', 'A Victorian surgeon rescues a heavily disfigured man being mistreated by his \"owner\" as a side-show freak. Behind his monstrous façade, there is revealed a person of great intelligence and sensitivity. Based on the true story of Joseph Merrick (called John Merrick in the film), a severely deformed man in 19th century London.', '24.669', '/rk2lKgEtjF9HO9N2UFMRc2cMGdj.jpg', '1980-10-09', 'The Elephant Man', 'false', '8.1', 2831),
(2457, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/59kBgtfbhh1dalgjGvFhDL98jN.jpg', '18,10749', 'fr', 'Filmed during the German occupation, this French milestone centers around the theatrical life of a beautiful courtesan and the four men who love her. Voted the “Best French Film in History” by the French Film Academy in 1990.', '9.593', '/yiy9stl1jjVhW44ypkWMFDT8Ix3.jpg', '1945-03-15', 'Children of Paradise', 'false', '8.2', 314),
(2517, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/dTL3unDQ9J3opvmjeSNC8MPUk5V.jpg', '18', 'ja', 'In a small Tokyo apartment, twelve-year-old Akira must care for his younger siblings after their mother leaves them and shows no sign of returning.', '24.990', '/kDUUdWrbBBVqzSmm27pHFJcTvCU.jpg', '2004-08-07', 'Nobody Knows', 'false', '8.0', 379),
(3082, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/kSlO1pHpwQfPQdgVPr7dJiJNtJ8.jpg', '35,18', 'en', 'The Tramp struggles to live in modern industrial society with the help of a young homeless woman.', '20.541', '/9xeglIbChLIe0P4fTQNAdlG2v0C.jpg', '1936-02-05', 'Modern Times', 'false', '8.3', 3107),
(3090, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/sj5R5SGor3YMFBuabMj8gPbyBmh.jpg', '12,18,37', 'en', 'Fred C. Dobbs and Bob Curtin, both down on their luck in Tampico, Mexico in 1925, meet up with a grizzled prospector named Howard and decide to join with him in search of gold in the wilds of central Mexico. Through enormous difficulties, they eventually succeed in finding gold, but bandits, the elements, and most especially greed threaten to turn their success into disaster.', '14.440', '/pWcst7zVbi8Z8W6GFrdNE7HHRxL.jpg', '1948-01-15', 'The Treasure of the Sierra Madre', 'false', '8.0', 942),
(3175, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/okdg55jhsr9k1F2lxsZoQncrLZL.jpg', '18,10749,10752', 'en', 'An Irish rogue uses his cunning and wit to work his way up the social classes of 18th century England, transforming himself from the humble Redmond Barry into the noble Barry Lyndon.', '15.624', '/A0byHUHMwZ7dtBQtfZ44QIgDbjo.jpg', '1975-11-26', 'Barry Lyndon', 'false', '8.0', 2327),
