(16672, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/oOM2JzhVBjWyZFHW2iBQQ8A3znY.jpg', '18,53', 'ja', 'An entomologist suffers extreme psychological and sexual torture after being taken captive by the residents of a poor seaside village.', '15.759', '/rE6vtXBDXy3cjyFmxfsDese0Eo4.jpg', '1964-02-15', 'Woman in the Dunes', 'false', '8.3', 312),
(16869, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/1Jpkm9qZcsT0mSyVXgs4VlGjPNI.jpg', '18,28,53,10752', 'en', 'In Nazi-occupied France during World War II, a group of Jewish-American soldiers known as \"The Basterds\" are chosen specifically to spread fear throughout the Third Reich by scalping and brutally killing Nazis. The Basterds, lead by Lt. Aldo Raine soon cross paths with a French-Jewish teenage girl who runs a movie theater in Paris which is targeted by the soldiers.', '68.104', '/7sfbEnaARXDDhKm0CZ7D7uc2sbo.jpg', '2009-08-19', 'Inglourious Basterds', 'false', '8.2', 19447),
(17663, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/55ZkbGyz6ls1ie217rqGpybQAOB.jpg', '10751,18', 'en', 'At the turn of the century on Prince Edward Island, Matthew Cuthbert and his sister Marilla decide to take on an orphan boy as help for their farm. But they get an unexpected jolt when they\'re mistakenly sent a girl instead: Anne Shirley.', '15.174', '/wuF8aapqbDPFkoWbwI5LWfDXpVq.jpg', '1985-12-01', 'Anne of Green Gables', 'false', '8.1', 207),
(18148, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/jLq0ol1f0ZKXni9R9GsPBcyPrNN.jpg', '18', 'ja', 'The elderly Shukishi and his wife, Tomi, take the long journey from their small seaside village to visit their adult children in Tokyo. Their elder son, Koichi, a doctor, and their daughter, Shige, a hairdresser, don\'t have much time to spend with their aged parents, and so it falls to Noriko, the widow of their younger son who was killed in the war, to keep her in-laws company.', '16.138', '/g2YbTYKpY7N2yDSk7BfXZ18I5QV.jpg', '1953-11-03', 'Tokyo Story', 'false', '8.3', 810),
(18438, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/q3cOyhojgMmgFjvLoyKDY8W3GP2.jpg', '18,35,10749', 'ko', 'Mr. Kim is jobless, lost in debt and has been dumped by his girlfriend. He decides to end it all by jumping into the Han River - only to find himself washed up on a small, mid-river island. He soon abandons thoughts of suicide or rescue and begins a new life as a castaway. His antics catch the attention of a young woman whose apartment overlooks the river. Her discovery changes both their lives.', '13.459', '/gGzovvmOEyNVUu4WEHtw9wfDsqI.jpg', '2009-05-14', 'Castaway on the Moon', 'false', '8.0', 556),
(18491, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/hyaLMOol8xju70zr5glK6JaprER.jpg', '18,16,878,28', 'ja', 'The second of two theatrically released follow-ups to the Neon Genesis Evangelion series. Comprising of two alternate episodes which were first intended to take the place of episodes 25 and 26, this finale answers many of the questions surrounding the series, while also opening up some new possibilities.', '37.822', '/j6G24dqI4WgUtChhWjfnI4lnmiK.jpg', '1997-07-19', 'Neon Genesis Evangelion: The End of Evangelion', 'false', '8.4', 1181),
(19404, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/vI3aUGTuRRdM7J78KIdW98LdxE5.jpg', '35,18,10749', 'hi', 'Raj is a rich, carefree, happy-go-lucky second generation NRI. Simran is the daughter of Chaudhary Baldev Singh, who in spite of being an NRI is very strict about adherence to Indian values. Simran has left for India to be married to her childhood fiancé. Raj leaves for India with a mission at his hands, to claim his lady love under the noses of her whole family. Thus begins a saga.', '28.779', '/2CAL2433ZeIihfX1Hb2139CX0pW.jpg', '1995-10-19', 'Dilwale Dulhania Le Jayenge', 'false', '8.6', 3956),
(19426, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/9yepEBnQNcKzWWyHdUiX8Mnqc6U.jpg', '18', 'it', 'Rome, 1957. A woman, Cabiria, is robbed and left to drown by her boyfriend, Giorgio. Rescued, she resumes her life and tries her best to find happiness in a cynical world. Even when she thinks her struggles are over and she has found happiness and contentment, things may not be what they seem.', '15.084', '/xF4oCG3PLNbcrtPZbqB3BtkIbKg.jpg', '1957-10-03', 'Nights of Cabiria', 'false', '8.1', 603),
(19542, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/cSbBSHHiy849SUhyTW6FX4Dbj43.jpg', '18,10749', 'en', 'In this classic drama, Vicky Page is an aspiring ballerina torn between her dedication to dance and her desire to love. While her imperious instructor, Boris Lermontov, urges to her to forget anything but ballet, Vicky begins to fall for the charming young composer Julian Craster. Eventually Vicky, under great emotional stress, must choose to pursue either her art or her romance, a decision that carries serious consequences.', '11.862', '/vPvpBWFWDvEXuQBkoYgA6A89GVp.jpg', '1948-09-06', 'The Red Shoes', 'false', '8.0', 484),
(20271, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/u2nPH7STKcz8ddpvxo8Ler1SvPc.jpg', '35', 'it', 'Ferdinando Cefalù is desperate to marry his cousin, Angela, but he is married to Rosalia and divorce is illegal in Italy. To get around the law, he tries to trick his wife into having an affair so he can catch her and murder her, as he knows he would be given a light sentence for killing an adulterous woman. He persuades a painter to lure his wife into an affair, but Rosalia proves to be more faithful than he expected.', '8.344', '/vZbdSpUFyFiDBBTY0AiSrN9f303.jpg', '1961-12-20', 'Divorce Italian Style', 'false', '8.0', 347),
(20334, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/wqgZSvgoctaadgwUdPYVsksivxn.jpg', '35,18,10749', 'en', 'Two employees at a gift shop can barely stand one another, without realising that they are falling in love through the post as each other\'s anonymous pen pal.', '19.446', '/dZ1aEzGYRiqJwPfjS6VL7wUkHmF.jpg', '1940-01-12', 'The Shop Around the Corner', 'false', '8.4', 558),
(20453, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/aFGPUmbgGoAt93WP3WYsAPa0Yv8.jpg', '18,35', 'hi', 'Rascal. Joker. Dreamer. Genius... You\'ve never met a college student quite like \"Rancho.\" From the moment he arrives at India\'s most prestigious university, Rancho\'s outlandish schemes turn the campus upside down—along with the lives of his two newfound best friends. Together, they make life miserable for \"Virus,\" the school’s uptight and heartless dean. But when Rancho catches the eye of the dean\'s sexy daughter, Virus sets his sights on flunking out the \"3 idiots\" once and for all.', '34.819', '/66A9MqXOyVFCssoloscw79z8Tew.jpg', '2009-12-23', '3 Idiots', 'false', '8.0', 1947),
(20530, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/mWRJfzYCQc1j8VYp3sRrwQIoJEo.jpg', '18', 'ja', 'Noriko is perfectly happy living at home with her widowed father, Shukichi, and has no plans to marry -- that is, until her aunt Masa convinces Shukichi that unless he marries off his 27-year-old daughter soon, she will likely remain alone for the rest of her life. When Noriko resists Masa\'s matchmaking, Shukichi is forced to deceive his daughter and sacrifice his own happiness to do what he believes is right.', '11.315', '/iNtRSY2AGjW1VDXDR79bKsNUdus.jpg', '1949-09-13', 'Late Spring', 'false', '8.0', 299),
(20532, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/d0IwJw1p2H0WYhk1iCwVNygpsUs.jpg', '18', 'ja', 'In medieval Japan a compassionate governor is sent into exile. His wife and children try to join him, but are separated, and the children grow up amid suffering and oppression.', '14.699', '/rSlZ8iM4vRM0sZrrJNmjln4kZir.jpg', '1954-03-31', 'Sansho the Bailiff', 'false', '8.2', 284),
(20803, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/z8125Gm4hadwQZOcFiZ7uor77E4.jpg', '35,878', 'ru', 'A scientist builds a time machine and accidentally sends his apartment complex manager and a petty burglar to 16th century Moscow, while Tsar Ivan the Terrible travels to 1973.', '13.076', '/6f7vhvnma8sbO6821ShE5ViA3r8.jpg', '1973-09-17', 'Ivan Vasilyevich Changes His Profession', 'false', '8.0', 266),
(20875, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/k9r86oHFo06ZC21zw2FkRD9wcJX.jpg', '35', 'ru', 'The film consists of three independent parts: \"Workmate\", \"Déjà vu\" and \"Operation Y\". The plot follows the adventures of Shurik (alternative spelling — Shourick), the naive and nerdy Soviet student who often gets into ludicrous situations but always finds a way out very neatly.  \"Operation Y and Shurik\'s Other Adventures\" was a hit movie and became the leader of Soviet film distribution in 1965.', '17.993', '/UObZrxhJklRmaOepUS9iTs9x4f.jpg', '1965-08-16', 'Operation Y and Other Shurik\'s Adventures', 'false', '8.0', 221),
(20914, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/bg4B52loVIYZTf3odGQKVV6B55h.jpg', '35', 'it', 'Four middle-aged friends in Florence organize together idle pranks (called zingarate, \"gypsy shenanigans\") in a continuous attempt to prolong childhood during their adult life.', '7.011', '/8Pm8SLjq2UHCwisd56ipHtzvZI1.jpg', '1975-10-24', 'My Friends', 'false', '8.2', 604),
(20941, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/89HE1VSdBDWBEro1wSpl2dFcfd9.jpg', '18,10752', 'es', 'A young boy, in an effort to have a normal childhood in 1980s El Salvador, is caught up in a dramatic fight for his life as he desperately tries to avoid the war which is raging all around him', '36.350', '/hvwB4LdMCLzqXsk5ZjR77vzPkGk.jpg', '2005-01-28', 'Innocent Voices', 'false', '8.1', 367),
(21634, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/pSjGsbqyKUzF8rHzL0vtVWV1pS6.jpg', '18,36,10770', 'en', 'Bobby Griffith was his mother\'s favorite son, the perfect all-American boy growing up under deeply religious influences in Walnut Creek, California. Bobby was also gay. Struggling with a conflict no one knew of, much less understood, Bobby finally came out to his family.', '16.672', '/1viFwXluAettogGDsTrSUUg29lZ.jpg', '2009-01-24', 'Prayers for Bobby', 'false', '8.1', 487),
(23282, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/fgKoKVw0f2X2ajilfoyra3LFrwo.jpg', '35', 'en', 'The story involves two newlyweds, Keaton and Seely, who receive a build-it-yourself house as a wedding gift. The house can be built, supposedly, in \"one week.\" A rejected suitor secretly re-numbers packing crates. The movie recounts Keaton\'s struggle to assemble the house according to this new \"arrangement.\"', '4.181', '/uNh7LyW43jkOPhqyuDIcMY0gVOg.jpg', '1920-08-29', 'One Week', 'false', '8.0', 203),
(24188, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/uUrV5KSjnZx47Dq7e6STr73iN4N.jpg', '18,35', 'it', 'Roberto, a shy law student in Rome, meets Bruno, a forty-year-old exuberant, capricious man, who takes him for a drive through the Roman and Tuscany countries in the summer. When their journey starts to blend into their daily lives though, the pair’s newfound friendship is tested.', '11.522', '/41BZ3auNuk5Hw6kKkxRPyOzXeqM.jpg', '1962-12-05', 'Il Sorpasso', 'false', '8.2', 599),
(24382, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/ryoWP1kvNcwPif6uNbuZwQfrJPy.jpg', '35,80', 'it', 'Best friends Peppe and Mario are thieves, but they\'re not very good at it. Still, Peppe thinks that he\'s finally devised a master heist that will make them rich. With the help of some fellow criminals, he plans to dig a tunnel from a rented apartment to the pawnshop next door, where they can rob the safe. But his plan is far from foolproof, and the fact that no one in the group has any experience digging tunnels proves to be the least of their problems.', '12.420', '/f5OxD8Nl0pR3DcYHtYhHRfpsmjl.jpg', '1958-07-26', 'Big Deal on Madonna Street', 'false', '8.1', 587),
(25237, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/oIQMt3Q6Qa37YD0JOdYkrIAPYDk.jpg', '18,10752', 'ru', 'The invasion of a village in Byelorussia by German forces sends young Florya into the forest to join the weary Resistance fighters, against his family\'s wishes. There he meets a girl, Glasha, who accompanies him back to his village. On returning home, Florya finds his family and fellow peasants massacred. His continued survival amidst the brutal debris of war becomes increasingly nightmarish, a battle between despair and hope.', '27.176', '/qNbMsKVzigERgJUbwf8pKyZogpb.jpg', '1985-07-09', 'Come and See', 'false', '8.3', 1030),
(25376, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/fNHCogWhABNAmzk0IFdzQP5XLYj.jpg', '80,9648,53,10749,18', 'es', 'A retired legal counselor writes a novel hoping to find closure for one of his past unresolved homicide cases and for his unreciprocated love with his superior - both of which still haunt him decades later.', '19.501', '/r3FctmAMk2tbrwxuWdpeLrZLwIz.jpg', '2009-08-13', 'The Secret in Their Eyes', 'false', '8.0', 2109),
(26022, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/fpgSkuEG2eV9nOHAYzqfOg1R8t2.jpg', '18,10749', 'hi', 'Rizwan Khan, a Muslim from the Borivali section of Mumbai, has Asperger\'s syndrome. He marries a Hindu single mother, Mandira, in San Francisco. After 9/11, Rizwan is detained by authorities at LAX who treat him as a terrorist because of his condition and his race.', '28.734', '/5Y36lCiNyyV71mjq6LavgiggbhT.jpg', '2010-02-10', 'My Name Is Khan', 'false', '8.0', 1078),
(26451, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/txKj2q2bBUl7KqPkcSx19qB7Ylw.jpg', '18,53', 'it', 'Rome, Italy. After committing a heinous crime, a senior police officer exposes evidence incriminating him because his moral commitment prevents him from circumventing the law and the social order it protects.', '12.751', '/vPTZwlq1IC4o1DCsEZEl2uGljzm.jpg', '1970-10-16', 'Investigation of a Citizen Above Suspicion', 'false', '8.2', 627),
(27205, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/s3TBrRGB1iav7gFOCNx3H31MoES.jpg', '28,878,12', 'en', 'Cobb, a skilled thief who commits corporate espionage by infiltrating the subconscious of his targets is offered a chance to regain his old life as payment for a task considered to be impossible: \"inception\", the implantation of another person\'s idea into a target\'s subconscious.', '85.537', '/8IB2e4r4oVhHnANbnm7O3Tj6tF8.jpg', '2010-07-15', 'Inception', 'false', '8.4', 32663);
INSERT INTO `films` (`id`, `adult`, `backdrop_path`, `genre_ids`, `original_language`, `overview`, `popularity`, `poster_path`, `release_date`, `title`, `video`, `vote_average`, `vote_count`) VALUES
(28178, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/y6JA85N8DvoonwqDGWlgkr1jnU.jpg', '18,10751', 'en', 'A drama based on the true story of a college professor\'s bond with the abandoned dog he takes into his home.', '44.285', '/lsy3aEsEfYIHdLRk4dontZ4s85h.jpg', '2009-06-08', 'Hachi: A Dog\'s Tale', 'false', '8.0', 5859),
(28422, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/jEnh78WU2kxjCFaCdRh2r6ZDbfP.jpg', '28,35,18,10749', 'ja', 'The story of a teenage boy named Yu, who falls for Yoko, a girl he runs into while working as an \"up-skirt\" photographer in an offshoot of the porn industry. His attempts to woo her are complicated by a spot of cross-dressing – which convinces Yoko that she is lesbian – dalliances with kung-fu and crime, and a constant struggle with the guilt that\'s a legacy of his Catholic upbringing.', '17.102', '/3QSGUdzG374H7pOxIdKNBpeLEUk.jpg', '2009-01-31', 'Love Exposure', 'false', '8.0', 347),
(28978, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/fSu9eMwiGR7YVznegeB4JQPKgrO.jpg', '35,10749', 'en', 'Charlie, a wandering tramp, becomes a circus handyman - soon the star of the show - and falls in love with the circus owner\'s stepdaughter.', '9.846', '/3FywbVq2qGqbYHPCy2NJcOf0gmp.jpg', '1928-01-06', 'The Circus', 'false', '8.0', 618),
(29259, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/f72GEQF2lKsdmEULSI9bWCbQylH.jpg', '80,18,53,36', 'fr', 'Four prison inmates have been hatching a plan to literally dig out of jail when another prisoner, Claude Gaspard, is moved into their cell. They take a risk and share their plan with the newcomer. Over the course of three days, the prisoners and friends break through the concrete floor using a bed post and begin to make their way through the sewer system -- yet their escape is anything but assured.', '15.574', '/8tAyoNf8M4nnMtjZ3RPwDJcx0yL.jpg', '1960-03-18', 'Le Trou', 'false', '8.3', 353),
(29264, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/mI7hfScSb8NAWC09viymxCzWZIq.jpg', '35,18,14', 'es', 'After a lavish dinner party, the guests find themselves mysteriously unable to leave the room.', '12.552', '/ttA4HFg4SaGWvE7dx5GLuYCvSiv.jpg', '1962-05-16', 'The Exterminating Angel', 'false', '8.0', 539),
(31414, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/5a4Gmk2HNeefI4Rmwdmbyoy79oy.jpg', '18', 'hu', 'Inhabitants of a small village in Hungary deal with the effects of the fall of Communism. The town\'s source of revenue, a factory, has closed, and the locals, who include a doctor and three couples, await a cash payment offered in the wake of the shuttering. Irimias, a villager thought to be dead, returns and, unbeknownst to the locals, is a police informant. In a scheme, he persuades the villagers to form a commune with him.', '10.385', '/y38z0v4HJ12MHiKddLEoFlvPiBt.jpg', '1994-02-08', 'Satantango', 'false', '8.2', 207),
(37165, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/jKpQiKPYNGBxjsrxZpMGTwggKw8.jpg', '35,18', 'en', 'Truman Burbank is the star of The Truman Show, a 24-hour-a-day reality TV show that broadcasts every aspect of his life without his knowledge. His entire life has been an unending soap opera for consumption by the rest of the world. And everyone he knows, including his wife and his best friend is really an actor, paid to be part of his life.', '53.045', '/vuza0WqY239yBXOadKlGwJsZJFE.jpg', '1998-06-04', 'The Truman Show', 'false', '8.1', 15467),
(37257, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/evUB9YKE5IPPtQOchcEF6hS90BO.jpg', '18,9648,80', 'en', 'When Leonard Vole is arrested for the sensational murder of a rich, middle-aged widow, the famous Sir Wilfrid Robarts agrees to appear on his behalf. Sir Wilfrid, recovering from a near-fatal heart attack, is supposed to be on a diet of bland, civil suits—but the lure of the criminal courts is too much for him, especially when the case is so difficult.', '18.612', '/mM5Cad2ESBprh6ucPnMzMfI34Cu.jpg', '1957-12-17', 'Witness for the Prosecution', 'false', '8.2', 1067),
(37793, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/7A7Zpru9lldnFsWOZQ8Fg63NUPj.jpg', '10402,27', 'en', 'In the town of Normal Valley, an eccentric magician named Maestro entertains the local children every day in his spooky mansion. One stormy night, the town\'s mayor leads a group of angry citizens to the mansion in an attempt to run Maestro out of town.', '6.632', '/yR5XSYPx6paPLPWMcPUHJBm1Vpb.jpg', '1997-09-04', 'Ghosts', 'false', '8.1', 201),
(38286, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/xhm7SfFI5ApWoqFVNnEnYxbIxJT.jpg', '35', 'it', 'Friends Aldo, Giovanni, and Giacomo travel from north to south for Giacomo\'s wedding, carrying a precious item: the father of the bride, a tyrannical rich man who is both their boss and father-in-law (also Aldo and Giovanni married his daughters), has entrusted them with a wooden leg, the work of a famous artist.', '7.273', '/qCw7fAZnA7DloKwvzdseWRYi19K.jpg', '1997-12-27', 'Three Men and a Leg', 'false', '8.0', 1886),
(38360, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/kmmt99iuCEm8iX39yxfqKu5xHGj.jpg', '18,10749,10752', 'ru', 'Veronika and Boris come together in Moscow shortly before World War II. Walking along the river, they watch cranes fly overhead, and promise to rendezvous before Boris leaves to fight. Boris misses the meeting and is off to the front lines, while Veronika waits patiently, sending letters faithfully. After her house is bombed, Veronika moves in with Boris\' family, into the company of a cousin with his own intentions.', '17.510', '/foXYOdXEJ0rvtTDo4LLnsUnvPLB.jpg', '1957-10-12', 'The Cranes Are Flying', 'false', '8.0', 265),
(40096, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/xs6awEGjnH3e36YSAromfYu3PBQ.jpg', '35,18,14', 'pt', 'The lively João Grilo and the sly Chicó are poor guys living in the hinterland who cheat a bunch of people in a small in Northeastern Brazil. When they die, they have to be judged by Christ, the Devil and the Virgin Mary before they are admitted to paradise.', '9.628', '/imcOp1kJsCsAFCoOtY5OnPrFbAf.jpg', '2000-09-15', 'A Dog\'s Will', 'false', '8.4', 930),
(42229, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/y5ebTEBtpLn8PprGTWQhDfq33k8.jpg', '18,10749', 'it', 'In Rome, fascist supporter Emanuele attends a parade commemorating Adolf Hitler\'s historic meeting with Italian leader Benito Mussolini, leaving his apolitical wife, Antonietta, to tend to household duties. Antonietta encounters a man, Gabriele, who appears surprisingly nonplussed by the political event. Over the course of the day, the two forge a close friendship that will forever change their perceptions of life, love and politics.', '7.301', '/mtJEhcmgqTIPyymRPZxqExSabrS.jpg', '1977-08-11', 'A Special Day', 'false', '8.1', 547),
(42269, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/2Kkqmy3EpXqBDqv1vvsNXX3pwww.jpg', '18,35', 'it', 'Three partisans bound by a strong friendship return home after the war, but the clash with everyday reality puts a strain on their bond.', '8.436', '/zGGWYpiKNwjpKxelPxOMqJnUgDs.jpg', '1974-12-21', 'We All Loved Each Other So Much', 'false', '8.3', 441),
