(334543, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/fgffluhvdOv79SkYaKrfRA0xkf4.jpg', '18', 'en', 'A five-year-old Indian boy gets lost on the streets of Calcutta, thousands of kilometers from home. He survives many challenges before being adopted by a couple in Australia; 25 years later, he sets out to find his lost family.', '26.250', '/kCELJH1tCmaRLqvwIgKDb09aEaw.jpg', '2016-11-24', 'Lion', 'false', '8.1', 5880),
(337404, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/6MKr3KgOLmzOP6MSuZERO41Lpkt.jpg', '35,80', 'en', 'In 1970s London amidst the punk rock revolution, a young grifter named Estella is determined to make a name for herself with her designs. She befriends a pair of young thieves who appreciate her appetite for mischief, and together they are able to build a life for themselves on the London streets. One day, Estella’s flair for fashion catches the eye of the Baroness von Hellman, a fashion legend who is devastatingly chic and terrifyingly haute. But their relationship sets in motion a course of events and revelations that will cause Estella to embrace her wicked side and become the raucous, fashionable and revenge-bent Cruella.', '193.215', '/wToO8opxkGwKgSfJ1JK8tGvkG6U.jpg', '2021-05-26', 'Cruella', 'false', '8.1', 7689),
(339877, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/kuOvQ9TqsZwleNVNmHRJiIyzsKx.jpg', '16,18,9648,36', 'en', 'A young man arrives at the last hometown of painter Vincent van Gogh to deliver the troubled artist\'s final letter and ends up investigating his final days there.', '17.721', '/56sq57kDm7XgyXBYrgJLumo0Jac.jpg', '2017-06-22', 'Loving Vincent', 'false', '8.1', 2157),
(347688, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/asiuMK2TcJGhbcn2dvHF2nLqpqw.jpg', '10751,16,35,9648', 'en', 'Get ready to Rock! Scooby-Doo and the Mystery Inc. Gang team up with the one and only KISS in this all-new, out-of-this-world adventure! We join the Gang at Kiss World – the all-things-Kiss theme park, as they investigate a series of strange hauntings. With help from Kiss, they discover that the Crimson Witch has returned to summon The Destroyer from the alternate dimension of Kissteria! The evil duos ghastly plan, to destroy the earth! Can the Gang\'s cunning and Kiss\'s power of rock save the day?!', '18.473', '/dubNbVmMmE9vULPA5CZokqUJ0o6.jpg', '2015-07-10', 'Scooby-Doo! and Kiss: Rock and Roll Mystery', 'false', '8.1', 244),
(354912, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/askg3SMvhqEl4OL52YuvdtY40Yb.jpg', '10751,16,14,10402,35,12', 'en', 'Despite his family’s baffling generations-old ban on music, Miguel dreams of becoming an accomplished musician like his idol, Ernesto de la Cruz. Desperate to prove his talent, Miguel finds himself in the stunning and colorful Land of the Dead following a mysterious chain of events. Along the way, he meets charming trickster Hector, and together, they set off on an extraordinary journey to unlock the real story behind Miguel\'s family history.', '186.298', '/gGEsBPAijhVUFoiNpgZXqRVWJt2.jpg', '2017-10-27', 'Coco', 'false', '8.2', 16529),
(359724, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/ydmZIafp66mHABs3QJDwvjRgZfE.jpg', '18,28,36', 'en', 'American car designer Carroll Shelby and the British-born driver Ken Miles work together to battle corporate interference, the laws of physics, and their own personal demons to build a revolutionary race car for Ford Motor Company and take on the dominating race cars of Enzo Ferrari at the 24 Hours of Le Mans in France in 1966.', '50.513', '/dR1Ju50iudrOh3YgfwkAU1g2HZe.jpg', '2019-11-13', 'Ford v Ferrari', 'false', '8.0', 6160),
(359940, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/oQHF0Y4gCw6VdPmapjsbZoxY2ht.jpg', '80,18', 'en', 'After seven months have passed without a culprit in her daughter\'s murder case, Mildred Hayes makes a bold move, painting three signs leading into her town with a controversial message directed at Bill Willoughby, the town\'s revered chief of police. When his second-in-command Officer Jason Dixon, an immature mother\'s boy with a penchant for violence, gets involved, the battle between Mildred and Ebbing\'s law enforcement is only exacerbated.', '26.429', '/vgvw6w1CtcFkuXXn004S5wQsHRl.jpg', '2017-12-01', 'Three Billboards Outside Ebbing, Missouri', 'false', '8.1', 8846),
(360814, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/5qjbu7po6eqLNd4kUPAyIpFRwQK.jpg', '18,10751,35,28', 'hi', 'Dangal is an extraordinary true story based on the life of Mahavir Singh and his two daughters, Geeta and Babita Phogat. The film traces the inspirational journey of a father who trains his daughters to become world class wrestlers.', '15.081', '/p2lVAcPuRPSO8Al6hDDGw0OgMi8.jpg', '2016-12-21', 'Dangal', 'false', '8.0', 759),
(361743, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/AaV1YIdWKnjAIAOe8UUKBFm327v.jpg', '28,18', 'en', 'After more than thirty years of service as one of the Navy’s top aviators, and dodging the advancement in rank that would ground him, Pete “Maverick” Mitchell finds himself training a detachment of TOP GUN graduates for a specialized mission the likes of which no living pilot has ever seen.', '543.544', '/62HCnUTziyWcpDaBO2i1DX17ljH.jpg', '2022-05-24', 'Top Gun: Maverick', 'false', '8.3', 4856),
(372058, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/mMtUybQ6hL24FXo0F3Z4j2KG7kZ.jpg', '10749,16,18', 'ja', 'High schoolers Mitsuha and Taki are complete strangers living separate lives. But one night, they suddenly switch places. Mitsuha wakes up in Taki’s body, and he in hers. This bizarre occurrence continues to happen randomly, and the two must adjust their lives around each other.', '95.561', '/q719jXXEzOoYaps6babgKnONONX.jpg', '2016-08-26', 'Your Name.', 'false', '8.5', 9252),
(372754, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/3RMLbSEXOn1CzLoNT7xFeLfdxhq.jpg', '10749,16', 'ja', 'Rihito Sajo, an honor student with a perfect score on the entrance exam and Hikaru Kusakabe, in a band and popular among girls, would have never crossed paths. Until one day they started talking at the practice for their school’s upcoming chorus festival. After school, the two meet regularly, as Hikaru helps Rihito to improve his singing skills. While they listen to each other’s voice and harmonize, their hearts start to beat together.', '17.624', '/cIfRCA5wEvj9tApca4UDUagQEiM.jpg', '2016-02-20', 'Dou kyu sei – Classmates', 'false', '8.5', 261),
(378064, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/q5HZvtyqG8Vz39Ee9uTQbLeEml.jpg', '16,18', 'ja', 'Shouya Ishida starts bullying the new girl in class, Shouko Nishimiya, because she is deaf. But as the teasing continues, the rest of the class starts to turn on Shouya for his lack of compassion. When they leave elementary school, Shouko and Shouya do not speak to each other again... until an older, wiser Shouya, tormented by his past behaviour, decides he must see Shouko once more. He wants to atone for his sins, but is it already too late...?', '73.847', '/tuFaWiqX0TXoWu7DGNcmX3UW7sT.jpg', '2016-09-17', 'A Silent Voice: The Movie', 'false', '8.4', 3181),
(378108, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/mNOB5JoW1imvdGrZ52RGZgJCop0.jpg', '18,16,10749,10752,36', 'ja', 'Japan, 1943, during World War II. Young Suzu leaves her village near Hiroshima to marry and live with her in-laws in Kure, a military harbor. Her creativity to overcome deprivation quickly makes her indispensable at home. Inhabited by an ancestral wisdom, Suzu impregnates the simple gestures of everyday life with poetry and beauty. The many hardships, the loss of loved ones, the frequent air raids of the enemy, nothing alters her enthusiasm…', '24.902', '/9Z4H4M2F8OQTB04YC1Opds8MFBb.jpg', '2016-11-12', 'In This Corner of the World', 'false', '8.0', 469),
(381284, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/rfkIeCaIHhN3K5wjJJqKmfUjYp8.jpg', '18,36', 'en', 'The untold story of Katherine G. Johnson, Dorothy Vaughan and Mary Jackson – brilliant African-American women working at NASA and serving as the brains behind one of the greatest operations in history – the launch of astronaut John Glenn into orbit. The visionary trio crossed all gender and race lines to inspire generations to dream big.', '83.031', '/9lfz2W2uGjyow3am00rsPJ8iOyq.jpg', '2016-12-10', 'Hidden Figures', 'false', '8.1', 8233),
(397567, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/wyv2Y9vXYJwJzF6cNVuVwVOsOUj.jpg', '18,14,28', 'ko', 'Having died unexpectedly, firefighter Ja-hong is taken to the afterlife by 3 afterlife guardians. Only when he passes 7 trials over 49 days and proves he was innocent in human life, he’s able to reincarnate, and his 3 afterlife guardians are by his side to defend him in trial.', '58.344', '/gJSvIsI6oQfFim0PGyuuiCYfqKs.jpg', '2017-12-14', 'Along with the Gods: The Two Worlds', 'false', '8.1', 726),
(398818, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/zvOJawrnmgK0sL293mOXOdLvTXQ.jpg', '10749,18', 'en', 'In 1980s Italy, a relationship begins between seventeen-year-old teenage Elio and the older adult man hired as his father\'s research assistant.', '76.141', '/gXiE0WveDnT0n5J4sW9TMxXF4oT.jpg', '2017-09-01', 'Call Me by Your Name', 'false', '8.2', 10687),
(399106, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/4GWYk5VP9qu1rNSeNAwNaBy9mwS.jpg', '10751,16', 'en', 'A mother bird tries to teach her little one how to find food by herself. In the process, she encounters a traumatic experience that she must overcome in order to survive.', '15.038', '/9tzpqQic0VJt4JCAJ5ZGrfs1qWV.jpg', '2016-06-16', 'Piper', 'false', '8.2', 1419),
(400608, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/nicDo6SnBxK93ROGAhpKTOAhy2i.jpg', '35,10402', 'en', 'Combining his trademark wit and self-deprecating humor with original music, Bo Burnham offers up his unique twist on life in this stand-up special about  life, death, sexuality, hypocrisy, mental illness and Pringles cans.', '6.788', '/1RqDE7X2rGjxKOklweUFd2U7Vn0.jpg', '2016-06-03', 'Bo Burnham: Make Happy', 'false', '8.1', 306),
(400928, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/gYtXT7fJNBRZBbBulO11DoRveLT.jpg', '18,35', 'en', 'Frank, a single man raising his child prodigy niece Mary, is drawn into a custody battle with his mother.', '49.768', '/9Ts7Vc4wLlpI9oox9mkVUE1tBHy.jpg', '2017-04-12', 'Gifted', 'false', '8.1', 4575),
(406997, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/b7xQ5fuyVO4c24igizCfPgF6n7q.jpg', '18,10751', 'en', 'The story of August Pullman – a boy with facial differences – who enters fifth grade, attending a mainstream elementary school for the first time.', '34.818', '/ouYgAatYH4JzIThj6FI3UYf31RI.jpg', '2017-11-13', 'Wonder', 'false', '8.2', 7082),
(411088, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/1ZSWFzAP4AZuFCigZZoib2RdcUO.jpg', '18,9648,53', 'es', 'Barcelona, Spain. Adrián Doria, a young and successful businessman accused of murder, meets one night with Virginia Goodman, an expert interrogation lawyer, in order to devise a defense strategy.', '37.863', '/fptnZJbLzKUHeNlYrAynbyoL5YJ.jpg', '2017-01-06', 'The Invisible Guest', 'false', '8.1', 3915),
(414419, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/itcAHIwxKvSkFEVUsqSpOEIRwZy.jpg', '28,80,53', 'en', 'An assassin is shot and almost killed by her ruthless employer, Bill, and other members of their assassination circle – but she lives to plot her vengeance.  Kill Bill: The Whole Bloody Affair is a complete edit of the two-part martial arts action films Kill Bill: Vol. 1 and Kill Bill: Vol. 2. The film was originally scheduled to be released as one part. However, due to the film\'s over 4 hour running time, it was split into two parts.', '18.840', '/zomX76Pf3nUaTzRBk5BveLk1QPu.jpg', '2011-03-27', 'Kill Bill: The Whole Bloody Affair', 'false', '7.9', 810),
(424694, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/7mmXWuBeNJiBO0NIOUWOuFve4Tb.jpg', '10402,18,36', 'en', 'Singer Freddie Mercury, guitarist Brian May, drummer Roger Taylor and bass guitarist John Deacon take the music world by storm when they form the rock \'n\' roll band Queen in 1970. Hit songs become instant classics. When Mercury\'s increasingly wild lifestyle starts to spiral out of control, Queen soon faces its greatest challenge yet – finding a way to keep the band together amid the success and excess.', '55.669', '/lHu1wtNaczFPGFDTrjCSzeLPTKN.jpg', '2018-10-24', 'Bohemian Rhapsody', 'false', '8.0', 15203),
(426618, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/jua8HIE1NaQp55rb4abecsQsSOm.jpg', '10752,18,10749', 'en', 'Germany, 1944. Leyna, the 15-year old daughter of a white German mother and a black African father, meets Lutz, a compassionate member of the Hitler Youth whose father is a prominent Nazi soldier, and they form an unlikely connection in this quickly changing world.', '15.879', '/omKzydOrom9kpdfQUE0G9Y9sPl0.jpg', '2018-09-14', 'Where Hands Touch', 'false', '8.0', 457),
(429210, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/dmsvUCbbAuxAFPj5QId0DlXLjvY.jpg', '35,18', 'pt', '1980s. Brazilian television exploding in color and auditorium programs not so politically correct. In the middle of this fervor, Augusto Mendes, a young rising actor, seeks his place in the sun. From porn studios to soap operas, he finally finds success and fame when he becomes \"Bingo\", a TV host clown from one of the audience leader TV shows for children. It turns out that behind the rice powder and red nose, nobody knows who he is.', '6.951', '/g4SKy57YSPraoOaZtrsuGhVzd0a.jpg', '2017-08-24', 'Bingo: The King of the Mornings', 'false', '8.0', 319),
(437068, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/eEJVX5w6rbeQGls3pNY7wYhB5YB.jpg', '28,18,36', 'ko', 'May, 1980. Man-seob is a taxi driver in Seoul who lives from hand to mouth, raising his young daughter alone. One day, he hears that there is a foreigner who will pay big money for a drive down to Gwangju city. Not knowing that he’s a German journalist with a hidden agenda, Man-seob takes the job.', '31.893', '/iXVaWbxmyPk4KZGZk5GGDGFieMX.jpg', '2017-08-02', 'A Taxi Driver', 'false', '8.1', 720),
(438695, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/6mJrgL7Mi13XjJeGYJFlD6UEVQw.jpg', '16,12,35', 'en', 'Buster and his new cast now have their sights set on debuting a new show at the Crystal Tower Theater in glamorous Redshore City. But with no connections, he and his singers must sneak into the Crystal Entertainment offices, run by the ruthless wolf mogul Jimmy Crystal, where the gang pitches the ridiculous idea of casting the lion rock legend Clay Calloway in their show. Buster must embark on a quest to find the now-isolated Clay and persuade him to return to the stage.', '201.481', '/aWeKITRFbbwY8txG5uCj4rMCfSP.jpg', '2021-12-01', 'Sing 2', 'false', '8.0', 3288),
(441130, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/yHtB4KHNigx3ZoxDvQbW2SOXGfq.jpg', '16,10751,12,14', 'en', 'In a time of superstition and magic, when wolves are seen as demonic and nature an evil to be tamed, a young apprentice hunter comes to Ireland with her father to wipe out the last pack. But when she saves a wild native girl, their friendship leads her to discover the world of the Wolfwalkers and transform her into the very thing her father is tasked to destroy.', '24.372', '/ehAKuE48okTuonq6TpsNQj8vFTC.jpg', '2020-10-26', 'Wolfwalkers', 'false', '8.3', 861),
(447362, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/88J6waYVTta8Qz3iX3qUeWNA5d5.jpg', '18,10749', 'en', 'A 17 year old finds out that his girlfriend is dying, so he sets out to give her an entire life, in the last year she has left.', '46.001', '/bP7u19opmHXYeTCUwGjlLldmUMc.jpg', '2020-11-27', 'Life in a Year', 'false', '8.3', 1170),
(449176, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/5VF2y1KyrrAL2WAX47odZ7TdelT.jpg', '35,18,10749', 'en', 'Everyone deserves a great love story. But for seventeen-year old Simon Spier it\'s a little more complicated: he\'s yet to tell his family or friends he\'s gay and he doesn\'t know the identity of the anonymous classmate he\'s fallen for online.', '29.214', '/5YUYg5q7QfC4IoNwNUtiwdiYKPr.jpg', '2018-02-16', 'Love, Simon', 'false', '8.1', 5518),
(455661, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/4datX8btikWEikf7esqEe6fhw.jpg', '10751,16,10749,35', 'en', 'A closeted boy runs the risk of being outed by his own heart after it pops out of his chest to chase down the boy of his dreams.', '5.814', '/wJUJROdLOtOzMixkjkx1aaZGSLl.jpg', '2017-06-01', 'In a Heartbeat', 'false', '8.0', 928),
(458220, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/bblKpucB0XbyQBmfXsaRN985Rgh.jpg', '18', 'en', 'After 12 years in prison, former high school football star Eddie Palmer returns home to put his life back together—and forms an unlikely bond with Sam, an outcast boy from a troubled home. But Eddie\'s past threatens to ruin his new life and family.', '30.530', '/xSDdRAjxKAGi8fUBLOqSrBhJmF0.jpg', '2021-01-29', 'Palmer', 'false', '8.1', 925),
(458302, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/4aFtD31RpP018y8XipTLrU8Y3pa.jpg', '12,10751,18', 'fr', 'At the age of 10 years, young Rémi is snatched from his adoptive mother and entrusted to the signor Vitalis, a mysterious itinerant musician. Has its hard sides - he will learn the harsh life of acrobat and sing to win his bread. Accompanied by the faithful dog capi and of the small monkey Joli-Coeur, his long trip through France, made for meetings, friendships and mutual assistance, leads him to the secret of its origins.', '14.053', '/mQYXlxlUTmOP4FWt52qkZZb8JNM.jpg', '2018-12-12', 'Remi, Nobody\'s Boy', 'false', '8.0', 354),
(470044, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/kH8xW7K2Gp1KOXoeewcLPkfqZ8K.jpg', '80,18', 'en', 'Raised in a poverty-stricken slum, a 16-year-old girl named Starr now attends a suburban prep school. After she witnesses a police officer shoot her unarmed best friend, she\'s torn between her two very different worlds as she tries to speak her truth.', '26.691', '/2icwBom0t5nmOuZI9FVXF3gkMK0.jpg', '2018-10-19', 'The Hate U Give', 'false', '8.2', 1845),
(472454, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/acqlcQWYE2F1ZRfS9dd4Mwb6BIO.jpg', '18,10752', 'tr', 'In 1950, amidst the ravages of the Korean War, Sergeant Süleyman stumbles upon a a half-frozen little girl, with no parents and no help in sight. Frantic, scared and on the verge of death, this little girl captures the heart of Süleyman, who risks his own life to save her, smuggling her into his Army base and out of harms way. Not knowing her name and unable to communicate with her, Süleyman names her Ayla, in reminiscence of the moon on the fateful night during which they met. The two form an instantaneous and inseparable bond, and Ayla, almost effortlessly, brings an uncanny joy to the Turkish brigade in the grip of war. As the war comes to a close however, Süleyman\'s brigade is told that they will be returning home. Süleyman cannot bear abandoning Ayla, and does everything within his power to take her with him. After repeated failure, he is forced to give Ayla to an orphanage, but doesn\'t give up on the hope of one day reuniting with her. Will the two ever get back together?', '23.162', '/pYhlkqBLMZuH8UmzTkENeSQ2vhb.jpg', '2017-10-27', 'Ayla: The Daughter of War', 'false', '8.1', 287),
(475557, 'false', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w220_and_h330_face/hO7KbdvGOtDdeg0W4Y5nKEHeDDh.jpg', '80,53,18', 'en', 'During the 1980s, a failed stand-up comedian is driven insane and turns to a life of crime and chaos in Gotham City while becoming an infamous psychopathic crime figure.', '120.816', '/udDclJoHjfjb8Ekgsd4FDteOkCU.jpg', '2019-10-01', 'Joker', 'false', '8.2', 21617);
